Sentencas: We report a cost-effective processing method for fabricating intermediate temperature solid oxide fuel cells (SOFCs) with Ni-samaria doped ceria (SDC) anode.
Titulo: Ni-SDC cermet anode fabricated from NiO-SDC composite powder for intermediate temperature SOFC

Sentencas: First, SDC and NiO powders were mechanically treated to make their composite powder.
Titulo: Ni-SDC cermet anode fabricated from NiO-SDC composite powder for intermediate temperature SOFC

Sentencas: Then, the composite powder was applied into a ceramic tape casting method to form a thick layer for the anode supporting.
Titulo: Ni-SDC cermet anode fabricated from NiO-SDC composite powder for intermediate temperature SOFC

Sentencas: Finally, an anode supported single cell with a configuration of Ni-SDC/SDC/La0.6Sr0.4CO0.2Fe0.8O3-delta (LSCF) was prepared.
Titulo: Ni-SDC cermet anode fabricated from NiO-SDC composite powder for intermediate temperature SOFC

Sentencas: Because of the usage of the composite powder, homogenous distribution and connection of each Ni and SDC were achieved.
Titulo: Ni-SDC cermet anode fabricated from NiO-SDC composite powder for intermediate temperature SOFC

Sentencas: Peak power densities of 460, 750 and 910mW cm(-2) were obtained on the single cell at 550, 600 and 650 degrees C, respectively.
Titulo: Ni-SDC cermet anode fabricated from NiO-SDC composite powder for intermediate temperature SOFC
